        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> Out of every piece of gear a Necro can obtain this is IMO the most important one.</P><P>Reasons why:</P><P>- .01 cast time.  Not instant, but damn close to it.</P><P>- You can feign death, clear aggro, get up and click this fast enough and the mobs won't see you.</P><P>- You can cast while running in the middle of KOS mobs and they won't care.</P><P>- Keeps a slot free for something else.</P><P>- Helps with quests, travel, etc.</P><P>- You can pull a mob and go invis all the way back to a spot and only bring that one you pulled.</P><P>- Same for root dotting - Cast your spells, and go invis.  Helps keeping adds away.</P><P>- Just the best damn item in game for us.  2nd best would have been the FD mask before the nerf.</P><P>There are some other issues I prob haven't mentioned here as well.  I almost lost mine when i inadvertantly gave it to someone while trading several things.  The person was kind enough to give it back as he had an SK with one, and realized the value of it.  I probably would have quit playing if I had lost it,  It is that important to me.</P><P><BR>Warlock of Terris-Thule</font></td>
